Recommends: gstreamer1.0-libav
Description: Internet radio player for Linux desktop
 PyRadio is a modern GTK4-based application for listening to internet
 radio stations. It provides:
  * Access to thousands of radio stations via RadioBrowser API
  * Support for Dutch and international stations
  * Favorites management
  * Display of current song/track information
  * Bitrate and codec information
  * Clean, intuitive GTK4 interface
  * Offline station caching
 .
 The application uses GStreamer for reliable audio playback and supports
 common streaming formats including MP3, AAC, and OGG.
